The second floor features 2 bedrooms, each with their own closet, and full bathroom. The third floor is the master bedroom suite with walk in closet. Master suite is complete with a balcony large enough for a table and two seats and features a beautiful view of center city. This home was fully renovated from top to bottom 5 years ago and has central air, new plumbing and electric, new vinyl windows, wide plank hardwood flooring, Hardie plank rear siding, and quality craftsmanship throughout.
